public class DataObjectView
extends org.eclipse.ui.part.ViewPart

This class is used to show the IntermediateDataObject view and also the tree view which contains group and classes.

This classes will contian fields with mapping information like database with IntermediateDataobject mapping and AtomicMetric with IntermediateDataObject.

This class will also generate the Java source code. Which will used for OJB

Author:
Maharajan, Debadatta Mishra
